reg_info.act_under: Ontario Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals Act

content.content: 1. (1) The information required to obtain a warrant under subsection 12 (1) of the Act shall be in Form 1. O. Reg. 266/99, s. 1 (1). (2) The warrant issued under subsection 12 (1) of the Act shall be in Form 2. O. Reg. 266/99, s. 1 (2).
content.raw_html:
1. (1) The information required to obtain a warrant under subsection 12 (1) of the Act shall be in Form 1. O. Reg. 266/99, s. 1 (1).

(2) The warrant issued under subsection 12 (1) of the Act shall be in Form 2. O. Reg. 266/99, s. 1 (2).
